{"tid":2080772,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想再係咁可以點","createTime":"2020-06-26T16:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T09:42:33.000Z","uid":189308,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a9fda0f876d1d63c0ba38719d6b8f2847edf3932","tid":2080772,"uid":189308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:12:18.000Z","msg":"頹咗好耐好耐喇<br />\n應該係時候要行返出嚟<br />\n但點解仲係好唔開心好想喊<br />\n好想幫自己 <br />\n但又唔知可以點<br />\n唔想再同人傾 好似講極都冇人明<br />\n跟住又開始慢慢疏遠哂身邊所有人<br />\n唔想覆msg 唔想出街<br />\n剩係想自己靜靜一個<br />\n好想換埋個電話號碼<br />\n等所有人都搵我唔到<br />\n唔洗強顏歡笑<br />\n唔洗同任何人交代<br />\n每日最開心既時間就係瞓著<br />\n可以咩都唔洗理<br />\n好似冇哂心機做任何野<br />\n有好多好崩潰既諗法<br />\n令我覺得自己唔可以再係咁<br />\n希望自己唔好再禁垃圾<br />\n<br />\n然後...<br />\n<br />\n聽朝瞓醒<br />\n我依然一樣<br />\n將自己困咗係一個好灰暗既地方<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b15cc3fca921c91ed56bf2cebc39a679dd1258","tid":2080772,"uid":360334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"唔好諗住自己係垃圾 因為更垃圾係到姐係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9ae9afe2c36e2da20a566165d2523aafea8498","tid":2080772,"uid":310504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"因咩事咁呀？"},{"pid":"6722742ea48f4590ad782c07db13f9cd3e86ccaf","tid":2080772,"uid":141951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:15:49.000Z","msg":"唔好逃避直視問題？"},{"pid":"9d59cd31fc965a1fcedf48a6b26152ceb1392c6d","tid":2080772,"uid":189308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74b15cc3fca921c91ed56bf2cebc39a679dd1258","tid":2080772,"uid":360334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"唔好諗住自己係垃圾 因為更垃圾係到姐係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"嗚 一齊去堆填區好冇"},{"pid":"788363849aaaa79e251f4cc6b46d667d7b104ede","tid":2080772,"uid":189308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p